Interface StreamBatchWriter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Channel, Closeable, WritableByteChannel

    public interface StreamBatchWriter
extends WritableByteChannel
    Used to write to Stream in Batch mode. Once closed, a new StreamBatchWriter needs to be created to do another set of batch writes.
